Package: NMRphasing
Type: Package
Title: Phase error correction and baseline correction for 1D NMR data
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Aixiang Jiang
Maintainer: Aixiang Jiang <aijiang@bccrc.ca> <aixiang.jiang@pathology.ubc.ca> 
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Suggests: knitr 
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: baseline, splines, MassSpecWavelet
Description: This package provides three types of phase error correction approaches:
    a) a single linear model with choices of several optimization functions
    b) multiple linear models with choices of several optimization functions
    c) shrinkage
    It also provides polynomial baseline correction.
